Package: ggCompNet
Type: Package
Title: Compare Timing of Network Visualizations in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Sam", "Tyner", email = "sctyner@iastate.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Heike", "Hofmann", email ="heike.hofmann@gmail.com", role= "aut")
  )
Description: The package has two purposes: 1) to provide a function to compare the speed of network drawing using several different packages, and 2) to host vignettes that provide code for reproducing examples in the paper "Network visualization with ggplot2" by Tyner et al. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: http://github.com/sctyner/ggCompNet
BugReports: https://github.com/sctyner/ggCompNet/issues
LazyData: TRUE
